 S Club 将发行 20 年来首张单曲，向乐队成员 Paul Cattermole 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-to-release-first-single-in-20-years-in-tribute-to-bandmate-paul-cattermole-3472593?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=s-club-to-release-first-single-in-20-years-in-tribute-to-bandmate-paul-cat特莫莱Anagricel DuranMon, 24 Jul 2023 19:22:33 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3472593 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing-.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 2 月 14 日在 Soho 酒店举行的“S Club 7 Reunited”重聚巡演。图片来源：Dave J. Hogan" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>歌曲《These Are The Days》将于 7 月 26 日发行</p><p>《Post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-to-release-first-single-in-20-years-in-tribute-to-bandmate-paul-cattermole-3472593">S Club》将发行 20 年来首张单曲，向乐队成员 Paul Cattermole 致敬，该单曲</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing-.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 2 月 14 日在 Soho 酒店举行的“S Club 7 Reunited”重聚巡演。图片来源：Dave J. Hogan" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/S-Club-7-posing--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/s-club-7">S Club</a>宣布他们将于本周发行一首新单曲，以纪念他们的前乐队成员、已故的保罗·卡特莫尔 (Paul Cattermole)。</p><p>该乐队已将名字从 S Club 7 调整为 S Club，并表示他们即将发行的歌曲“These Are The Days”将于 7 月 26 日星期三发行。</p><p>这首歌由五位现任乐队成员蒂娜·巴雷特、乔恩·李、布拉德利·麦金托什、乔·奥米拉和雷切尔·史蒂文斯演唱，向他们的“前朋友”和“挚爱”乐队成员卡特莫尔致敬。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/23150045/s-club-first-new-single-paul-cattermole-tribute/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《太阳报》报道</em></a>，这首歌将伴随一个“感人的电影故事，最后以 S Club 揭晓他们今天的五人流行组合”。该出版物还透露，一位知情人士表示，新单曲“听起来像是经典，将与他们的旧曲调完美契合”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cu7LcreoxjV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xm